searchData={"items":[{"type":"module","title":"TunnelProxy.AgentManager","doc":"Agent 注册 / 认证 / 心跳","ref":"TunnelProxy.AgentManager.html"},{"type":"function","title":"TunnelProxy.AgentManager.authenticate/2","doc":"","ref":"TunnelProxy.AgentManager.html#authenticate/2"},{"type":"function","title":"TunnelProxy.AgentManager.heartbeat/2","doc":"","ref":"TunnelProxy.AgentManager.html#heartbeat/2"},{"type":"function","title":"TunnelProxy.AgentManager.init_preset_agent/0","doc":"","ref":"TunnelProxy.AgentManager.html#init_preset_agent/0"},{"type":"function","title":"TunnelProxy.AgentManager.list_all/0","doc":"","ref":"TunnelProxy.AgentManager.html#list_all/0"},{"type":"function","title":"TunnelProxy.AgentManager.lock_registration/0","doc":"","ref":"TunnelProxy.AgentManager.html#lock_registration/0"},{"type":"function","title":"TunnelProxy.AgentManager.register/2","doc":"","ref":"TunnelProxy.AgentManager.html#register/2"},{"type":"function","title":"TunnelProxy.AgentManager.registration_locked?/0","doc":"","ref":"TunnelProxy.AgentManager.html#registration_locked?/0"},{"type":"function","title":"TunnelProxy.AgentManager.unlock_registration/0","doc":"","ref":"TunnelProxy.AgentManager.html#unlock_registration/0"},{"type":"module","title":"TunnelProxy.Cache","doc":"","ref":"TunnelProxy.Cache.html"},{"type":"function","title":"TunnelProxy.Cache.generations/0","doc":"A convenience function for retrieving the current generations.","ref":"TunnelProxy.Cache.html#generations/0"},{"type":"function","title":"TunnelProxy.Cache.new_generation/1","doc":"A convenience function for creating new generations.","ref":"TunnelProxy.Cache.html#new_generation/1"},{"type":"function","title":"TunnelProxy.Cache.newer_generation/0","doc":"A convenience function for retrieving the newer generation.","ref":"TunnelProxy.Cache.html#newer_generation/0"},{"type":"function","title":"TunnelProxy.Cache.reset_generation_timer/0","doc":"A convenience function for reset the GC timer.","ref":"TunnelProxy.Cache.html#reset_generation_timer/0"},{"type":"module","title":"TunnelProxy.PTYGateway","doc":"纯 BEAM 内部一次性 PTY 会话。\n使用环境变量中的 Agent Token 直接认证，认证通过后动态分配端口并启动临时 PTY 服务器。\n客户端 10 秒内 `nc localhost  ` 即可进入 fish shell。","ref":"TunnelProxy.PTYGateway.html"},{"type":"function","title":"TunnelProxy.PTYGateway.request_session/1","doc":"","ref":"TunnelProxy.PTYGateway.html#request_session/1"},{"type":"module","title":"TunnelProxy.PTYPool","doc":"每个 agent_id 对应一个持久 ExPTY shell 进程。\nshell 在 agent 首次 exec 时懒创建，exit 后自动从 pool 移除。","ref":"TunnelProxy.PTYPool.html"},{"type":"function","title":"TunnelProxy.PTYPool.child_spec/1","doc":"Returns a specification to start this module under a supervisor.\n\nSee `Supervisor`.","ref":"TunnelProxy.PTYPool.html#child_spec/1"},{"type":"function","title":"TunnelProxy.PTYPool.exec/3","doc":"向 agent 的 PTY 会话提交命令，返回 {:ok, task_id} 或 {:error, :busy}","ref":"TunnelProxy.PTYPool.html#exec/3"},{"type":"function","title":"TunnelProxy.PTYPool.init/1","doc":"Callback implementation for  GenServer.init/1 .","ref":"TunnelProxy.PTYPool.html#init/1"},{"type":"function","title":"TunnelProxy.PTYPool.kill/1","doc":"强制终止 agent 的 shell 会话","ref":"TunnelProxy.PTYPool.html#kill/1"},{"type":"function","title":"TunnelProxy.PTYPool.start_link/1","doc":"","ref":"TunnelProxy.PTYPool.html#start_link/1"},{"type":"module","title":"TunnelProxy.ResultCollector","doc":"双哨兵·深度堆栈管理（极简固定哨兵）。\n\n哨兵：\n    左哨兵: ꧁\n    右哨兵: ꧂\n\n规则：\n    - 每个哨兵在PTY输出中出现2次（回显 + 实际输出）。\n    - 有效计数 = 出现次数 ÷ 2。\n    - depth = 有效左 - 有效右。\n    - depth: 0→1 开始收集，1→0 完成收集。\n    - 使用字节级切片 (:binary.part) 避免 UTF-8 偏移问题。","ref":"TunnelProxy.ResultCollector.html"},{"type":"function","title":"TunnelProxy.ResultCollector.collect/2","doc":"","ref":"TunnelProxy.ResultCollector.html#collect/2"},{"type":"function","title":"TunnelProxy.ResultCollector.get/1","doc":"","ref":"TunnelProxy.ResultCollector.html#get/1"},{"type":"function","title":"TunnelProxy.ResultCollector.init_task/1","doc":"","ref":"TunnelProxy.ResultCollector.html#init_task/1"},{"type":"function","title":"TunnelProxy.ResultCollector.sentinel_left/0","doc":"","ref":"TunnelProxy.ResultCollector.html#sentinel_left/0"},{"type":"function","title":"TunnelProxy.ResultCollector.sentinel_right/0","doc":"","ref":"TunnelProxy.ResultCollector.html#sentinel_right/0"},{"type":"module","title":"TunnelProxy.Router","doc":"Bandit/Plug HTTP 路由。\n\nAgent API：\n  POST /api/register        注册 agent，返回 token\n  POST /api/heartbeat       心跳保活\n  POST /api/exec            提交命令，返回 task_id\n  GET  /api/result/:task_id 轮询执行结果\n  GET  /api/agents          列出所有 agent（管理用）\n  DELETE /api/agents/:id    强制终止 agent 的 shell\n\n文件服务器（保留原有功能）：\n  GET  /upload              上传页面\n  POST /upload              二进制上传（magic-word 协议）\n  GET  /proxy?url=...       HTTP 反向代理\n  GET  /*                   静态文件 / 目录列表","ref":"TunnelProxy.Router.html"},{"type":"function","title":"TunnelProxy.Router.call/2","doc":"Callback implementation for  Plug.call/2 .","ref":"TunnelProxy.Router.html#call/2"},{"type":"function","title":"TunnelProxy.Router.init/1","doc":"Callback implementation for  Plug.init/1 .","ref":"TunnelProxy.Router.html#init/1"},{"type":"module","title":"TunnelProxy.TaskExecutor","doc":"GenStage 消费者：从队列拉取任务并交给 PTYPool 执行","ref":"TunnelProxy.TaskExecutor.html"},{"type":"function","title":"TunnelProxy.TaskExecutor.handle_events/3","doc":"Callback implementation for  GenStage.handle_events/3 .","ref":"TunnelProxy.TaskExecutor.html#handle_events/3"},{"type":"function","title":"TunnelProxy.TaskExecutor.init/1","doc":"Callback implementation for  GenStage.init/1 .","ref":"TunnelProxy.TaskExecutor.html#init/1"},{"type":"function","title":"TunnelProxy.TaskExecutor.start_link/1","doc":"","ref":"TunnelProxy.TaskExecutor.html#start_link/1"},{"type":"module","title":"TunnelProxy.TaskQueue","doc":"GenStage 生产者：命令任务队列","ref":"TunnelProxy.TaskQueue.html"},{"type":"function","title":"TunnelProxy.TaskQueue.handle_cast/2","doc":"Callback implementation for  GenStage.handle_cast/2 .","ref":"TunnelProxy.TaskQueue.html#handle_cast/2"},{"type":"function","title":"TunnelProxy.TaskQueue.handle_demand/2","doc":"Callback implementation for  GenStage.handle_demand/2 .","ref":"TunnelProxy.TaskQueue.html#handle_demand/2"},{"type":"function","title":"TunnelProxy.TaskQueue.init/1","doc":"Callback implementation for  GenStage.init/1 .","ref":"TunnelProxy.TaskQueue.html#init/1"},{"type":"function","title":"TunnelProxy.TaskQueue.push/1","doc":"","ref":"TunnelProxy.TaskQueue.html#push/1"},{"type":"function","title":"TunnelProxy.TaskQueue.start_link/1","doc":"","ref":"TunnelProxy.TaskQueue.html#start_link/1"},{"type":"module","title":"TunnelProxy.Application","doc":"","ref":"TunnelProxy.Application.html"},{"type":"function","title":"TunnelProxy.Application.start/2","doc":"Callback implementation for  Application.start/2 .","ref":"TunnelProxy.Application.html#start/2"},{"type":"extras","title":"README","doc":"---\nTunnelProxy\n\nHTTP Server + PTY Shell Forwarder + Agent C2 Framework\n\nA lightweight all-in-one tool for file serving, remote shell, file upload, and persistent agent-controlled PTY sessions. Designed for AI cloud sandbox escape via FRP intranet penetration.\n\nFeatures\n\nFeature Description\nStatic File Server Browse and download files with directory listing\nPTY Shell Forwarder Persistent shell per agent + one-time temporary shell sessions\nFile Upload Upload via web page or curl command\nAgent Management Register, heartbeat, remote command execution with token auth\nOne-Time PTY Session Dynamic random port, token-authenticated, 10s auto-destroy\nRegistration Lock Prevent new agent registration in production\nPreset Agents Auto-register agents from environment variables on startup\n---\nInstallation\n\nOption 1: Install from Hex\n\n```elixir\ndef deps do\n  [\n    {:tunnel_proxy, \"~> 0.3.3\"}\n  ]\nend\n```\n\nOption 2: Build from Source\n\n```bash\ngit clone https://github.com/TurinFohlen/tunnel_proxy.git\ncd tunnel_proxy\nmix deps.get\nmix compile\n```\n\nQuick Start\n\nStart the Server\n\n```bash\nexport TUNNEL_DOC_ROOT=\"./www\"\nexport TUNNEL_UPLOAD_DIR=\"./uploads\"\nexport TUNNEL_PRESET_AGENT_1=\"agent1:myhost:root:linux\"\nmkdir -p \"$TUNNEL_DOC_ROOT\" \"$TUNNEL_UPLOAD_DIR\"\niex -S mix\n```\n\nExpected output:\n\n```\n[AgentManager] Preset agent registered: agent1\n[AgentManager] Token: xxxxxxxxx\nHTTP Server: 0.0.0.0:8080\n```\n\nConnect to Persistent Shell (nc)\n\n```bash\n# First request a one-time PTY session with your agent token\ncurl -X POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/session \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"token\":\"你的token\"}'\n# Returns {\"ok\":true,\"port\":45231}\n\n# Then connect within 10 seconds\nnc 127.0.0.1 45231\n```\n\nType commands and get output:\n\n```bash\n$ pwd\n/path/to/current\n$ ls -la\n...file list...\n$ exit\n```\n\nExecute Commands via HTTP API\n\n```bash\n# Execute a command\ncurl -X POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/exec \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"agent_id\":\"agent1\",\"token\":\"你的token\",\"cmd\":\"whoami\"}'\n# Returns {\"ok\":true,\"task_id\":\"agent1_1\"}\n\n# Get result\ncurl http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/result/agent1_1\n# Returns {\"output\":\"root\",\"status\":\"complete\"}\n```\n\nAccess Files\n\n```bash\ncurl http://127.0.0.1:8080/\n```\n\nOpen in browser: http://127.0.0.1:8080/\n\nUpload Files\n\nVia curl:\n\n```bash\ncurl -X POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/upload --data-binary @file.txt\n```\n\nVia browser:\nVisit http://127.0.0.1:8080/upload, select file, click upload.\n\nAgent API Reference\n\nMethod Path Description\nPOST /api/register Register a new agent\nPOST /api/heartbeat Agent heartbeat keep-alive\nPOST /api/exec Submit a command for execution\nGET /api/result/:task_id Poll command execution result\nGET /api/agents List all online agents\nPOST /api/session Request a one-time PTY session port\n\nConfiguration\n\nCreate config/config.exs or set environment variables:\n\n```elixir\nconfig :tunnel_proxy,\n  http_port: 8080,\n  doc_root: \"./www\",\n  upload_dir: \"./uploads\"\n```\n\nEnvironment variables:\n\nVariable Default Description\nTUNNEL_PRESET_AGENT_1 - Preset agent 1 (id:hostname:username:os)\nTUNNEL_PRESET_AGENT_2 - Preset agent 2 (optional)\nTUNNEL_LOCK_REGISTRATION - Set to 1 to prevent new agent registration\nSHELL /bin/sh Shell to use for PTY sessions\nUPLOAD_MAGIC MY_MAGIC_2025_FILE_HEAD Magic word for upload validation\nTUNNEL_DOC_ROOT ./www Static files directory\nTUNNEL_UPLOAD_DIR ./uploads Upload destination\n\nUse Cases\n\nStandalone\n\n```bash\ncd ~/tunnel_proxy\nexport TUNNEL_PRESET_AGENT_1=\"main:localhost:root:linux\"\niex -S mix\n```\n\nWith frp (Intranet Penetration)\n\nCreate a setup script that generates a secure, unique FRP configuration:\n\n```bash\ncat > setup-frp.sh << 'SETUP_EOF'\n#!/bin/bash\nFRPC_CONFIG=\"frpc.toml\"\nPROXY_NAME=\"tunnel-$(openssl rand -hex 32)\"\nHTTP_PORT=$((10001 + RANDOM % 40000))\nSHELL_PORT=$((10001 + RANDOM % 40000))\nwhile [ $SHELL_PORT -eq $HTTP_PORT ]; do\n    SHELL_PORT=$((10001 + RANDOM % 40000))\ndone\n\ncat > \"$FRPC_CONFIG\" < \ncurl http://frp.freefrp.net: /\n```\n\nRequirements\n\n· Elixir 1.12+\n· Erlang/OTP 24+\n\nLicense\n\nMIT License - see LICENSE file for details.\n\nAuthor\n\nTurinFohlen - GitHub\n\nContributing\n\nIssues and pull requests are welcome.","ref":"readme.html"}],"proglang":"elixir","producer":{"name":"ex_doc","version":"0.40.1"},"content_type":"text/markdown"}